product_name: Timbuk2 Elise Mini Duffel Bag - Women's
long_description: Throw the women's Elise Mini Duffel Bag from Timbuk2 over your shoulder and head out the door for whatever adventures await. Durable fabric and webbing straps are a hallmark of Timbuk2 bags. External pocket holds your phone. Internal zippered organizer pocket secures small items; key fob clips your keys so you never have to dig for them. The Elise Mini Duffel Bag from Timbuk2 features a unique gathered design, refined metal hardwear and a printed liner for a quality feel.
